HEADWORD: Sevenscore
<hw>Sev"en*score`</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n. & a.</pos> <def>Seven times
twenty, that is, a hundred and forty.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>The old Countess of Desmond . . . lived <qex>sevenscore</qex>
years.</q> <rj><qau>Bacon.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Seven-shooter</ent>⟦br⟧
